#  Delivery & Logistics Performance Analysis Dashboard | Power BI Project

##  Project Overview

This project presents an interactive **Delivery & Logistics Performance Dashboard** built using **Power BI** to analyze shipment operations, delivery efficiency, route performance, and logistics KPIs. The dashboard enables logistics managers and business stakeholders to monitor key performance metrics, identify operational bottlenecks, and improve delivery performance through data-driven decision-making.

---

##  Business Problem

Logistics companies often face challenges in tracking delivery performance across different routes and shipment types. Without a centralized reporting solution, management teams struggle to:

* Monitor on-time delivery performance.
* Identify delayed shipments and bottlenecks.
* Track distance coverage and route efficiency.
* Analyze cutoff compliance across days and time slots.
* Compare planned route metrics with actual delivery outcomes.

This dashboard provides a single source of truth for monitoring logistics operations and improving service efficiency.

---

##  Dashboard KPIs

| KPI                    | Description                               |
| ---------------------- | ----------------------------------------- |
| Total Shipments        | Total number of shipments processed       |
| Average Delivery Time  | Average delivery duration in minutes      |
| Total Distance Covered | Total distance traveled by shipments      |
| On-Time Delivery %     | Percentage of shipments delivered on time |
| Delayed Shipment %     | Percentage of delayed deliveries          |

